item.title: About
item.description: Preserving A Valuable Resource The internet today is filled with endless hours worth of inspirational and motivational content. However this poses a problem as a viewer can become overwhelmed with the decision of what to watch and how to apply what they watch. The goal of this archive is to focus on collecting the before mentioned content on the internet, filter the best parts, and centralize critical knowledge of today’s world.
